snippet.textDisplay:
It's 6th July , 
I listened whole song whle crying loudly in my room...with the thought of ....  thinking to end my life , due to not being sucessful, lack of support from family, no one try to understand your feelings, it's all about money , all other things are meaningless without money . if you don't have money , no one will care for your , no one will love you. 
    All I want is just for once someone try to understand me , respect my feelings , appreciate my efforts ..... 
I am Hindu , but now I not belive in any god/allah, nor in any religion, there is no such god I think , but I think there is some kind of energy the lyrics is begging for that energy ...... i m beliving in that same energy , after listning this song I decided to give one try this year I should give one more attempt , I don't know know what will happen next But I trust that one energy whoever god, jesus, allah is there , whatever his shape.... 
I hope when I visit this comment section after a year I will be happy and sucessfull.  
thakns for this song ... 💌
